{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1329,"text":"The shocking police crackdown\non protestors in Ferguson, Missouri,"},{"time":5717,"text":"in the wake of the police \nshooting of Michael Brown,"},{"time":8729,"text":"underscored the extent to which advanced\nmilitary weapons and equipment,"},{"time":12952,"text":"designed for the battlefield,"},{"time":14684,"text":"are making their way"},{"time":15993,"text":"to small-town police departments\nacross the United States."},{"time":20514,"text":"Although much tougher to observe,"},{"time":22500,"text":"this same thing is happening \nwith surveillance equipment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26047,"text":"NSA-style mass \nsurveillance is enabling"},{"time":28707,"text":"local police departments \nto gather vast quantities"},{"time":31665,"text":"of sensitive information\nabout each and every one of us"},{"time":35232,"text":"in a way that was\nnever previously possible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39284,"text":"Location information can \nbe very sensitive."},{"time":42760,"text":"If you drive your car around\nthe United States,"},{"time":45391,"text":"it can reveal if you go \nto a therapist,"},{"time":47314,"text":"attend an Alcoholics Anonymous meeting,"},{"time":49782,"text":"if you go to church \nor if you don't go to church."},{"time":52603,"text":"And when that \ninformation about you"},{"time":54329,"text":"is combined with the same information\nabout everyone else,"},{"time":57824,"text":"the government can gain \na detailed portrait"},{"time":60398,"text":"of how private citizens interact."}]},{"cues":[{"time":63114,"text":"This information used to be private."},{"time":65589,"text":"Thanks to modern technology,"},{"time":67282,"text":"the government knows far too much\nabout what happens behind closed doors."},{"time":71610,"text":"And local police departments make\ndecisions about who they think you are"},{"time":75998,"text":"based on this information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79169,"text":"One of the key technologies \ndriving mass location tracking"},{"time":83816,"text":"is the innocuous-sounding\nAutomatic License Plate Reader."},{"time":86774,"text":"If you haven't seen one,"},{"time":88469,"text":"it's probably because you didn't\nknow what to look for --"},{"time":91657,"text":"they're everywhere."},{"time":93032,"text":"Mounted on roads or \non police cars,"},{"time":96104,"text":"Automatic License Plate Readers\ncapture images of every passing car"},{"time":100533,"text":"and convert the license plate\ninto machine-readable text"},{"time":104158,"text":"so that they can be checked\nagainst hot lists"},{"time":107560,"text":"of cars potentially wanted\nfor wrongdoing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110845,"text":"But more than that, increasingly,"},{"time":112972,"text":"local police departments \nare keeping records"},{"time":115122,"text":"not just of people wanted for wrongdoing,"},{"time":118282,"text":"but of every plate that \npasses them by,"},{"time":121084,"text":"resulting in the collection\nof mass quantities of data"},{"time":125053,"text":"about where Americans have gone."},{"time":127294,"text":"Did you know this\nwas happening?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":129822,"text":"When Mike Katz-Lacabe asked\nhis local police department"},{"time":133228,"text":"for information about the plate\nreader data they had on him,"},{"time":136657,"text":"this is what they got:"},{"time":138335,"text":"in addition to the date, \ntime and location,"},{"time":141477,"text":"the police department had \nphotographs that captured"},{"time":144508,"text":"where he was going and \noften who he was with."},{"time":147898,"text":"The second photo from the top\nis a picture of Mike and his two daughters"},{"time":151720,"text":"getting out of their car\nin their own driveway."},{"time":155552,"text":"The government has \nhundreds of photos like this"},{"time":158340,"text":"about Mike going about his daily life."},{"time":161111,"text":"And if you drive a car \nin the United States,"},{"time":163295,"text":"I would bet money \nthat they have photographs"},{"time":166028,"text":"like this of you going\nabout your daily life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":168946,"text":"Mike hasn't done anything wrong."},{"time":170987,"text":"Why is it okay that the government\nis keeping all of this information?"},{"time":174942,"text":"The reason it's happening is because,"},{"time":176721,"text":"as the cost of storing\nthis data has plummeted,"},{"time":180072,"text":"the police departments\nsimply hang on to it,"},{"time":182584,"text":"just in case it could be useful someday."},{"time":186366,"text":"The issue is not just that\none police department"},{"time":188866,"text":"is gathering this information in isolation"},{"time":191487,"text":"or even that multiple police \ndepartments are doing it."},{"time":194246,"text":"At the same time, the federal government"},{"time":196743,"text":"is collecting all of these\nindividual pots of data,"},{"time":200361,"text":"and pooling them together \ninto one vast database"},{"time":203682,"text":"with hundreds of millions of hits,"},{"time":205338,"text":"showing where Americans have traveled."},{"time":207806,"text":"This document from the \nFederal Drug Enforcement Administration,"},{"time":210964,"text":"which is one of the agencies\nprimarily interested in this,"},{"time":213729,"text":"is one of several that reveal \nthe existence of this database."},{"time":218166,"text":"Meanwhile, in New York City,"},{"time":220735,"text":"the NYPD has driven police cars\nequipped with license plate readers"},{"time":224677,"text":"past mosques in order to\nfigure out who is attending."}]},{"cues":[{"time":228851,"text":"The uses and abuses of this technology\naren't limited to the United States."},{"time":232689,"text":"In the U.K., the police department"},{"time":235724,"text":"put 80-year-old John Kat\non a plate reader watch list"},{"time":239868,"text":"after he had attended dozens of\nlawful political demonstrations"},{"time":244145,"text":"where he liked to sit on a bench\nand sketch the attendees."}]},{"cues":[{"time":248771,"text":"License plate readers aren't the\nonly mass location tracking technology"},{"time":252293,"text":"available to law enforcement agents today."},{"time":254449,"text":"Through a technique known as\na cell tower dump,"},{"time":257461,"text":"law enforcement agents can\nuncover who was using"},{"time":260713,"text":"one or more cell towers\nat a particular time,"},{"time":262998,"text":"a technique which has been known to reveal"},{"time":265030,"text":"the location of tens of thousands\nand even hundreds of thousands of people."},{"time":269309,"text":"Also, using a device known as a StingRay,"},{"time":272549,"text":"law enforcement agents\ncan send tracking signals"},{"time":275185,"text":"inside people's houses\nto identify the cell phones located there."},{"time":279550,"text":"And if they don't know\nwhich house to target,"},{"time":281812,"text":"they've been known \nto drive this technology"},{"time":283998,"text":"around through whole neighborhoods."}]},{"cues":[{"time":287424,"text":"Just as the police in Ferguson possess\nhigh-tech military weapons and equipment,"},{"time":292060,"text":"so too do police departments across\nthe United States"},{"time":295042,"text":"possess high-tech surveillance gear."},{"time":297377,"text":"Just because you don't see it,"},{"time":299408,"text":"doesn't mean it's not there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301793,"text":"The question is, what should\nwe do about this?"},{"time":304344,"text":"I think this poses a serious\ncivil liberties threat."},{"time":307654,"text":"History has shown that once the police \nhave massive quantities of data,"},{"time":312016,"text":"tracking the movements of innocent people,"},{"time":314095,"text":"it gets abused, maybe for blackmail,\nmaybe for political advantage,"},{"time":318411,"text":"or maybe for simple voyeurism."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320670,"text":"Fortunately, there are steps we can take."},{"time":323012,"text":"Local police departments can \nbe governed by the city councils,"},{"time":326742,"text":"which can pass laws requiring the police"},{"time":329664,"text":"to dispose of the data \nabout innocent people"},{"time":332586,"text":"while allowing the legitimate\nuses of the technology to go forward."},{"time":335748,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":337423,"text":"(Applause)."}]}]}